APEX CODE TO FIND AREA OF CIRCLE
======================================================================

public class basic 
{
    public static void base()
    {
      integer a = 7;
      Decimal area;
      area = 3.14 * a * a;
      system.debug('AREA OF CIRCLE : ' +area);
        
    }

}

======================================================================

TO EXECUTE USE THE FOLLOWING COMMAND

basic.base();

======================================================================
